CAN_CLC

"MultiCAN Clock Control Register"

AddressCAN_CLC_ADDR = 0xF0004000
Absolute addressableNo
Reset value0x00000003
C typeCAN_CLC_t

CAN_CLC.bits "MultiCAN Clock Control Register"
Bit field #Bits Bits' position Mask Name Mask Access Shift (LSB)
